<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body style="font-family: sans-serif; max-width: 480px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 20px; background: #fff;">
  <h1 style="font-size: 28px;">🎉 Party Voting!</h1>
  <p>Hey <%= @guest.email %>,</p>
  <p>Click the button below to cast your votes at the party!</p>
  <p style="text-align:center; margin: 32px 0;">
    <a href="<%= @url %>" style="background:#7c3aed;color:#fff;padding:16px 32px;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-size:18px;font-weight:bold;">
      Vote Now!
    </a>
  </p>
  <p style="color:#888;font-size:12px;">This link expires in 30 minutes. If you didn't request this, ignore this email.</p>
</body>
</html>
